This application implements the OpenWOP v1 wire contract and consumes the
published @openwop/openwop SDK. The protocol specification itself lives in
openwop/openwop (Apache-2.0 for code, CC BY 4.0 for the spec prose).

Third-party components retain their own licenses (see each dependency's package
metadata) — notably the Lucide icon set (Apache-2.0), re-exported under
frontend/react/src/ui/icons/.
